##In Wuhan, the center of the epidemic storm, the shop that once held our joys and sorrows still perseveres stubbornly

WECHAT betteryourlife2013

The introduction to better your life focuses on the better you and the better world that comes with it.

The new crown epidemic raging, to all walks of life have caused not small impact, enterprises have lit up the red light.

"Cash won't last three months, " SIBE's former boss said in an interview video, before the one-way Street Bookstore crowdfunded via official Wechat. These high-profile brands can still be heard through the media or ask for help, and the street shop owners, especially the Wuhan entrepreneurs at the heart of the epidemic storm, have to digest the crisis alone.

Cherry blossom, the spring arrived, the epidemic bullet hit the shop has been staying in the cold winter. Anxiety, loss, helplessness, at a loss... entrepreneurs have more complex than ordinary people.

We found seven young people in Wuhan familiar with the entity store owner, whether it is standing more than 20 years old store, or newly opened not long, "the epidemic of survival" is their common test.







When the outbreak began, most people thought the disaster would be over in a month or so, and those who were normally busy at work simply consoled themselves by taking a long vacation.

With all the bad news coming in, people just can't keep their heads down. The most serious period of time, visual bookstore manager Duan Chengbo also insomnia, until the eight support came to Wuhan, the mood slowly stable.

New Year's Day in Zhongshan Road, outside the shop of the American Academy of Visual Arts

"Try not to read the news, then adjust your state. Get up regularly, eat, work, and slowly forget that you are locked up. " Many people are like Yuxin coffee manager and half-owner, when you get rid of negative news, you start to become positive.

Years ago the heart checked out the overworked half-moon boss, in the period of forced rest, found that quiet thinking is also a good thing.

In addition to trying to placate the small partners left alone, half the boss is also very worried about their mental health, long time at home life, it is easy to cause day and night reversal, distraction. So he began to do online training, regularly called everyone together, on the one hand training theory, on the one hand, let everyone have something to do every day, guide everyone to maintain a regular schedule and maintain a good mental state.

Friends from Cafe Youxin

Monday, the chain with the most stores, was the best of the interviewees'hearts, with her dishes Ogawa and AK. In Acre. Lab Yangfeng has six restaurants in Wuhan. "We all know that it's hard to cook, and we never have a long vacation, so I hope the staff can have a good rest this time. "

For herself, it was the first time in a decade that she had taken nearly two months off. She was locked at home every day busy vegetables, play online script to kill, but also learned to do chop pepper fish head, spicy spicy pot..

Also optimistic is the boss of the HK restaurant, master Liu, as the chef in the shop, "professional convenience" so that she can prepare a good meal every day, and occasionally do some dessert drinks. Even when she had a light breakfast, she ate it as delicately as she could, with coffee or milk tea, and cooked her own bread to perfection.

Master Liu's breakfast

In contrast, Lu Lu Lu, the owner of Luji, who lives in a Golden Lake, was not so "lucky. " Her cousin had a mild illness and was cured after treatment, but her uncle's illness has been recurrent since he was infected. The old uncle, who used to be in the Air Force, is now as thin as a bone, he's still in the ICU. While thinking about how to save their shop, because their relatives infected with the disease, Lu Lu also suffered from the new crown brought by the mental torture.

Xu Dao, who returned to his hometown in Shandong Province before the closure of the city, was also worried every day. She felt that Tanhualin store would have to wait until the summer, when the Cherry Blossom Festival and the May Day peak season were missed.

In addition to the flower cake shop and the Tongluoshao shop in Tanghualin, Xu Dao also has a Taobao shop selling pajamas. The logistics that used to take three or four days now take half a month to arrive, causing her to be constantly scolded by buyers, even though she has many ideas now, i can't. I can't.

"Xu Dao dao and her Gong Shao" hand-painted storefront

"Tanhualin's most awesome store is just a small one with little risk resistance. I now envy the 9-to-5 workers. If someone asked me to do something else for a profitable sideline, I would say yes right away. " Or that heroic Xu Dao dao dao dao.

People who make food and drink, every day in the guess after the epidemic everyone will be "revenge consumption" or "not consumption. Xu Dao knew that the flower cakes and gongs she sold were non-essential goods. This outbreak made her shop go straight to "death" from a healthy baby that was thriving. When Xu Dao heard other shops had closed down before, he felt that it didn't matter, now I know what it's like.

As the siege grew longer and longer, it became clear that this would be the biggest crisis most businessmen have ever faced.

You Xin cafe has never had a long holiday since it opened. In July and December last year, they opened Hanjie and no pressure exploration stores, both of which are still in the investment and adjustment phase, the sudden outbreak of the disease, the company's cash flow is stretched thin.

Yoshin's coffee, Han Street, lakeside

The half monthly boss conservatively estimates that they have lost more than 500,000 yuan since the closure of the city. The loss is also a large waste of food, the original plan for the Spring Festival four stores normal business, so double the production of a lot of dessert, but also a lot of coffee stocks. After they decided to close the door, they donated all the biscuits, candy, ear bags and so on to the nearest South Central Hospital.

"Now the biggest problem is the rent, labor, and after the resumption of start-up capital. " Think of these, half the boss can only reluctantly scratch his head.

Rent is the first knife in the neck of most businessmen, Xu Dao now every day to open his eyes will think he has four rents to pay in Wuhan: Two Shops, an office, a residence.

By early March, her losses were between $700,000 and $100,000. If she doesn't fully recover by May or June, the losses are estimated to be around $300,000. Xu Dao did not go for rent relief, first, because she knew that with Tan Hualin's sister-in-law said that these are impossible, usually they will only want to do all the reasons to increase the rent. And because she doesn't know how hard it is for other people.

SASAGAWA & ACRE's boss, Monday, said the main expenses for the restaurant were rent and wages, and that they were losing about half a million dollars a month.

Monday"calls for landlords with the ability to offer relief, but not moral kidnapping. "A lot of landlords are commercial real estate, and they have loans to pay back, so you have to put yourself in their shoes. One size does not fit all. "

Sweet aunt's secret dish Taishingli

For sweet aunt private kitchen, road goods set, HK restaurant in the old concession area of Hankou, because the property is mostly private, negotiate with the landlord rent-free is almost impossible.

The boss is also the employee's shop, the work stop is zero income. And with the rent and utilities still to be paid, it's overwhelming.

Lu Wu Ji Han Kou Dian

Duan Chengbo, who runs the bookstore, has less to lose than Lu Lu, who does jewelry design. After all, there is no loss of ingredients. The former has a monthly loss of about eighty thousand; the latter has a monthly loss of about 20,000.

Unlike a day job, which brings in revenue every day, she normally makes fifty thousand a month, and when she stops, her cash flow dries up and the whole operation is disrupted.

Lu Wu Ji Wen Hua bookstore

Those who work are rich in the new year, those who do business are poor in the new year. Just before the Spring Festival last year, Kelu had only a few thousand yuan in his hand after settling his account. Because the jewelry industry is very high pressure goods, plus years ago also prepared a lot of goods, such as this is the season of Spring Festival, Valentine's Day, International Women's Day, Wuhan's Cherry Blossom Festival, and then to the summer is off-season.

Kelu also has a bed-and-breakfast, but the tourism industry has been hit hard, so when the closure is lifted, she will consider returning the bed-and-breakfast House. In an interview, Kelu revealed that she had borrowed 30,000 yuan from alipay's online business, a loan that paid no interest and allowed her to take a breather.

Not long ago, a well-known bookstore in Beijing issued a "letter of help" to the community and their fans, Duan Chengbo felt that this is a kind of emotional marketing, is an overdraft of the future..

The bookshops around the country are all talking about self-help after the outbreak. Each store has different characteristics, can go down and live a good store, must have "content force" , "private area flow" , "creativity" , this is Duan Chengbo bookstore after years of experience.

Visual bookstore creative world shop

Outside Hubei, many places have resumed work. How are they doing? Kelu's friends in Guangzhou told her that although the jewelry market in Guangzhou had opened, there was no one in the stalls. The area as big as eight Guanggu squares was now empty. The workers in the processing plant had not fully resumed their work and business could not be carried out.

Clurben thought he was already miserable, but there were many more miserable people around, "My dad owns a mixing plant, and it's been two years since the construction started, and now it's finally working, and it's happening again, and more than 100 tons of cement in his warehouse are about to expire. If we don't do it, we'll lose money."

Kelu also has a friend who runs a chain of coffee shops. One branch of Kelu in Hong Kong alone is losing 80,000 yuan a month.

Sweet aunt and "Monday" also said that many friends around the store are almost unable to survive, one is because the business situation before the epidemic is not optimistic, closing is timely stop losses, and another is expanding too fast, cash flow was wiped out after the outbreak.

People used to come and go, Tanhualin

"The owner of Tan Hualin would complain to each other in the group, and everyone seemed to be in a miserable situation. In the group, the message used to be 'drink in my shop' , 'I've painted a new picture' , but now it's 'I'm going to sell the shop out' . ". Xu Dao described the exchange as a superficial expression of emotion, and did not discuss how to do.

Xu Dao dao's good friend da Shui Ren in Chongqing, Xu Dao envies that he can still draw body-building, but she worries about a variety of issues every day. She and the old staff and partners also maintain a tacit understanding, their own circle like, also talk about some gossip, but really put the "survival of the store" on the table talk, the silence.

At the end of last year, Visual Bookstore signed a new 400-square-meter store near the store. According to the original plan, the store should have moved to expand earlier this year, but now it has to wait.

"We are a traditional book store with a history of 22 years, " he said. "We are well known in the Wuhan Art Circle. If we don't make some changes, we will eventually be eliminated. " Even without the epidemic, duan Chengbo has also been thinking about the way forward.

The American Academy of Visual Arts

Also on the HSINTIEN agenda are auntie sweet and Monday, the new Hsintien on Youth Road, which signed a contract years ago to finish the renovation, and a larger garden flagship store project, ogawa and Acre had plans for two new stores this year, but now everyone is slowing down.

In order to survive, not long after the closure of the city, "Monday" began to lay off staff. Of course, most of those who were laid off had shorter hours and wanted to leave. But those who have a hard time at home and work long hours will be guaranteed a salary.

Monday also decided to give staff a lesson on borrowing and overspending after the epidemic was over and she would teach them how to manage their finances.

Akak.lab Korean cuisine with ocean breeze

The epidemic lasted too long, and some old employees who could not return to Wuhan said they would quit their jobs and go home after the epidemic was over. Sweet aunt felt that this situation was a great loss for them, because it is not easy to train a good old employee, this is more than a material loss. In addition, sweet aunt also said that if can survive this hurdle, the first thing to open the business is to let profits, let life more small surprises.

Xu, who has been riding a wave of success, said that if he survived this time, he would step up his propaganda again. "I was too stuck in my ways before, and I thought it would be OK if I didn't lose money. After the epidemic ends, I have to go back to the state of just starting a business, and everything goes back to zero. "

The Popular Gong burning before the epidemic

A few days ago, an old customer who left Wuhan after graduation sent a message to Xu Dao saying, "don't wait for me to go back to Wuhan and I won't see your shop again. " This made her sigh with emotion. If the capital chain really breaks, she will abandon her car and protect the commander in chief, at least one of the stores.

Miserable, some people are still optimistic about the future, half the boss and partners believe that the core competitiveness of Youxin will not change, the right opportunity, you may be able to see the new shop.

A concert at the Youxin cafe

Better: it's been so long since I've been to the store. What do I miss most?

Sweet aunt: Because the shop is my own decoration, recently also in mind where to change, where to repair. I want to work, I want to wait tables, I want to talk to people.

Xu Dao: want to party with old friends of Tan Hua Lin, Miss Huang boss's excellent cooking skills, want to go to his free meal, drink big wine. Miss Tan Hualin people to come and go: flirtatious lovers, walk the old man, knitting sister-in-law, sitting in the corner of the pony in the sun, running dog. But this is as old as the last century.

Half-moon boss: I always think of the regular beach concerts held by Youxin Qingshan Ben Giang Shop. On the quiet bank of the Yangtze River, under the beautiful setting sun, my friends and guests drink their favorite coffee and sing charming songs.

Better: Is there anything else you'd like to say?

Duan Chengbo: during the epidemic, Japanese designer Akira Kurokawa's "eight aesthetic senses of Japan" , which refers to "one period and one meeting" , explains the author in this way: The moment that can communicate with this person now, will not come again. Don't take a long term view of what meeting this person means to you, whether it's good for you in the future, or whether it's good for you in the future.

Right now, this moment, this relationship with this person, that's all that matters. And that's what I feel most about this outbreak!

Sweet Aunt: I'm actually worried about whether I can keep the income and future of the old staff after the epidemic, after all, the salary of the service industry staff is not high, behind is to support the family. On the other hand, if the post-80s people in Wuhan are old enough to say that they have experienced any special period, I am afraid it will be this time.

Monday: In the lyrics of "Beneath the Lion Rock" , "when we all meet under Sierra Leone, we laugh more than we sob. Life is hard and it's hard not to worry. " The hope is that when the seal is lifted, to make up for all the family photos we missed last year.

In-house food for HK restaurant

Offline activities of Visual Library

-

When I asked Xu Dao what else want to say to you, the phone that very loudly back to a "I want to ask you, remember Tan Hualin Xu Dao it. ".

Of course we remember, remember Tanhualin's big water and Xu Dao dao dao, remember master Zhao and uncle Qin Fei of Liangdao Street, remember the three dogs and Jiang Po of Lanling Road, remember the snail God and Master Liu of Cai e Lu, remember master Dong and the eldest son of station road, i remember the Lilac and Beer commune on Garden Road, the Balinese and Xia style of the ten thousand Pines Garden, the eighteen tavern and UNCLE g of Dazhi road, the small square and five Zhong of Honggang City, the Chuan Mei and Zhou Ji of Kirin road, the Yishan and Combo of Lingjiao Lake, remember the VOX and the prison in Ludlow..

There are too many stores worth keeping in mind. We hope that every store carrying Wuhan's early morning or late night, loneliness or joy, three meals, four seasons or idealism can be well managed. After the epidemic, everyone's hearts and stomachs need to be comforted.
